15/*! \file */
16
17#include <config.h>
18
19#include <isc/util.h>
20
21#include <isccfg/log.h>
22
23/*%
24 * When adding a new category, be sure to add the appropriate
25 * \#define to <isccfg/log.h>.
26 */
27LIBISCCFG_EXTERNAL_DATA isc_logcategory_t cfg_categories[] = {
28 { "config", 0 },
29 { NULL, 0 }
30};
31
32/*%
33 * When adding a new module, be sure to add the appropriate
34 * \#define to <isccfg/log.h>.
35 */
36LIBISCCFG_EXTERNAL_DATA isc_logmodule_t cfg_modules[] = {
37 { "isccfg/parser", 0 },
38 { NULL, 0 }
39};
40
41void
42cfg_log_init(isc_log_t *lctx) {
43 REQUIRE(lctx != NULL);
44
45 isc_log_registercategories(lctx, cfg_categories);
46 isc_log_registermodules(lctx, cfg_modules);
47}
